course_title: Graduate Practicum in Nursing - GRAD PRAC NURS

sections.comments: Pre-requisite: NURS 520To register please contact academic.support@nursing.ubc.ca, Student Services will contact the instructor  and  graduate program coordinator to facilitate permission.Title: Leadership development and administration within the Graduate Student Nursing Association (GSNA)A practicum course in administration and leadership co-designed by Professor Maura MacPhee and Graduate Student Nursing Association (GSNA) officers. Course participants will be expected to attend GSNA leadership meetings and participate in GSNA event and symposium planning.
